results.name: Expansion of the polynomial (1+x^3)*(1+x^5)*(1+x^7)*(1+x^9)*(1+x^11)*(1+x^13)*(1+x^15).
comment: This is the Poincaré polynomial for the Lie group A_7.
reference: Borel, A. and Chevalley, C., The Betti numbers of the exceptional groups, Mem. Amer. Math. Soc. 1955, no. 14, pp 1-9.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 25 2010
